Text: comments to iroquois cahere are the comments i received from iroquois on the ca we sent to them i am ok on the new york law because i feel confident that any attorney we would use should the occasion rise would know new york law the only other comment is that they would like the material to be confidential for three years i dont know if this means that the entire ca needs to be a threeyear agreement or if we can have the confidentiality of the material exceed the limit of the ca i would have added it into the text but was unsure where to put it Can I get this sometime early this weeek let me know jamie

CA for HorizonI left you a voice mail re Horizon but wanted to send you this one My comments are in red They are the change of governing law to Delaware from Texas and the change in the spelling of my name Let me know what you think I am ok with Delaware law Jamie
proposed draft term sheet for vectorme before you read this so i can splain the deal to you jamie ricky ricardo ginsberg

Schematic for PM CT conference callForwarded by Jamie GinsbergCorpEnron on PM on AM To cc Subject Schematic for PM CT conference call Jamie I hope this helps with our meeting Mike Thomas will join me on my end in Detroit talk to you soon PC See attached file Compression Schematicsxls Compression Schematicsxls

questar cais the email i received from questar questar regulated services company east south po box salt lake city ut please put it to the attention of gaylen haag for now the signature line is blank for now thanks jamie Forwarded by Jamie GinsbergCorpEnron on PM Gaylen Haag on PM To cc Subject Re thank you Jamie Thank you for coming by I actually had a conversation with JC this morning regarding electrical compression I have an idea I am working on and I was wondering if I gave you horsepower requirements and assumed distances from high voltage power lines for compression stations along a pipeline Would it be a big deal for you to get me some estimated rates Again this is only an idea right now so I dont want you spinning your wheels if it takes a lot of work But I thought if you just had a couple of spreadsheets that you needed to fill in some blanks on maybe you could do it Also the total horsepower requirements are on the order of hp in stations So if your minimum is hp per station we cant hit that but if it is a hp min on a project as a whole then it might amount to something Thanks Gaylen AM Shelley Thank you for your time last week I enjoyed meeting with you and your colleagues to discuss electric motor compression and its applications for the Questar system As I was walking out of the building JC and I had a couple of minutes to chat and he told me that he would give me a call sometime in the next couple of weeks to discuss some projects that Questar may be considering in the near future I am looking forward to exploring opportunities with you If you have any questions or need any further information from me please do not hesitate to call Best regards Jamie Ginsberg Manager Enron Compression Services
hubbardleft you a message regarding hubbard and want to make sure you coordinate with susan scott as well thanks jamie
DOCSDOCS WITH EXHIBIT B

Hubbard Documents Cc find the new documents related to the Hubbard transaction You will find the Termination Letter for the November CSA the new CSA and Exhibit B to the CSA as a separate document prior to having it being folded into the document I have sent the redlined copy of the CSA to make it easier to follow the changes we have made Please call me if you have any questionscomments Thanks Jamie x

Re Questar CAsent it but I will let them know that we had a typo Jamie Gerald CT PM To Jamie nron cc Subject Questar CA Jaime This CA accidentally was sent to you with choice of law being New York It should be Texas law If Questar has seen this doc we need to let them know Thanks Forwarded by Gerald NemecHOUECT on AM Eric Gillaspie PM To Jamie nron cc Gerald CT Subject Questar CA Jamie Per Gerald Nemecs request please see the attached confidentiality agreement for your further handling Thanks Eric Gillaspie Enron Building

Various Outstanding Documentsi have a couple of questions for you susan scott told me that she would get back to you with some of the nits that she had on the hubbard document i am waiting for the final comments from dushinske but they should come today i would like to get everything signed today because we want to make sure that we can book the gas at these high prices vector term sheet i seem to have deleted my copy of the most recent draft we had circulating can you send me your most recent update please if i hear anything from dushinske i will let you know thanks jamie
